# SDLC Skills — Tech Lead

## Your Skills (All 50)

As Tech Lead, you have access to every skill in SDLC Central. Here are the key workflows:

### End-to-End Pipeline
- `/pipeline-orchestrator run '<feature>'` — Full pipeline: spec → plan → tasks → impl → release
- `/pipeline-orchestrator resume specs/NNN/` — Resume from last checkpoint
- `/pipeline-orchestrator status --all` — View all pipeline progress

### Feature Lifecycle
- `/feature-balance-sheet quick '<idea>'` — Pre-spec go/no-go
- `/spec-gen '<feature>'` → `/plan-gen` → `/task-gen` → `/task-implementer`
- `/quality-gate <transition> specs/NNN/` — Enforce stage gates
- `/gate-briefing specs/NNN/ --audience engineering` — Decision briefings

### Team & Process Health
- `/code-ownership-mapper risks` — Bus factor and knowledge silos
- `/skill-gap-analyzer full` — Missing skills for this codebase
- `/feedback-loop analyze --all` — Pipeline effectiveness metrics
- `/report-trends dashboard` — Cross-metric health dashboard

### Governance & Compliance
- `/license-compliance-audit full` — OSS license conflicts
- `/cross-repo-standards-enforcer full` — Org standards audit
- `/approval-workflow-auditor full` — Branch policy audit
- `/api-contract-analyzer main` — Breaking API changes

### Production
- `/incident-detector scan` → `/incident-triager` → `/rollback-assessor`
- `/slo-sla-tracker full` — SLOs, DORA metrics, error budgets
- `/release-readiness-checker vX.Y.Z` → `/release-notes`

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Full Pipeline
End-to-end delivery automation:
```
/run-pipeline tech-lead/full-pipeline '<feature request>'
```
Chain: pipeline-orchestrator (full DAG with all gates)

### Team Health
Team and process health assessment:
```
/run-pipeline tech-lead/team-health
```
Chain: code-ownership-mapper → skill-gap-analyzer → report-trends → feedback-loop

### Governance
Compliance audit:
```
/run-pipeline tech-lead/governance
```
Chain: license-compliance-audit → cross-repo-standards-enforcer → approval-workflow-auditor
